channel.description:
Adds a double XP ring for your server, if you'd like to have one

Find
[code=java]amount *= Config.SERVER_EXP_BONUS;[/code]

where your source handles server experience. You might have a better chance searching for
[code]EXP[/code]
if you cannot find the other piece.

Replace with:
[code=java]		if (c.playerEquipment[c.playerRing] == 6465) //your ring ID here
		{ 
			amount *= Config.SERVER_EXP_BONUS * 4;
		} else {
			amount *= Config.SERVER_EXP_BONUS;
		}
		if (c.playerEquipment[c.playerRing] == 4202) //your ring ID here
		{ 
			amount *= Config.SERVER_EXP_BONUS * 2;
		} else {
			amount *= Config.SERVER_EXP_BONUS;
		}[/code]

Can be improved with an array if you want.
[code=java]int[] xpRings = { xpRing1, xpRing2 };[/code]

